&lt;div&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Linux&#34; src=&#34;/images/content/unsplash-wallpapers-linux.gif&#34; data-caption=&#34;Linux&#34; data-fancybox=&#34;gallery&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
