&lt;h3 id=&#34;下載&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#下載&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;下載&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;下載&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;下載點請到 &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/soroushchehresa/unsplash-wallpapers/releases&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;nexmoefont icon-github&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Github Release&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;依據你的系統下載定應安裝檔&lt;br&gt;&lt;img onerror=&#34;imgOnError(this);&#34; data-fancybox=&#34;gallery&#34; src=&#34;/images/content/unsplash-wallpaper-release.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;release&#34; data-caption=&#34;release&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
